dataStoreTool.description:
This Data Store contains Knowledge Base documents that answer general questions for different values of `brand_code` (i.e. different company brands that are managed by the same agent). A filter like the following MUST be included when querying the Data Store: "brand_code: ANY(\"$BRAND_CODE\")". For example, this would be an invocation payload for the Cymbal Telecom brand:

{
    "query": query,
    "filter": "brand_code: ANY(\"cymbal\")"
  }
